[
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_4630_0",
    "text": "前言",
    "canon_role": "section_header",
    "bbox": [
      0.032995875515560553,
      0.017777777777777778,
      0.11648543932008498,
      0.09155555555555556
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_4630",
    "order": 1
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_4630_1",
    "text": "“作死”这个词不好听，但绝非危耸听，认真读完，你就信了。给以提示，给 高三学生以警醒！",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.022997125359330083,
      0.09777777777777778,
      0.9593800774903137,
      0.20355555555555555
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_4630",
    "order": 2
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_4630_2",
    "text": "高考作有特殊的写作情境，高考阅卷也有特殊的批改背景。个省几十万份试卷，要 在短短几天内完成，阅卷老师要看得准还要看得快，平均一天看几百近千篇文章。压力大， 任务重，可想而知。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.0254968128983877,
      0.2311111111111111,
      0.9488813898262717,
      0.3973333333333333
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_4630",
    "order": 3
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_4630_3",
    "text": "• 亲历多年考阅卷的师如是说：开始阅卷天，热情满腔，上荣光，“为国选材” ；慢慢地，头晕脑胀，习以为常，“杀如麻”，话说得有些让悚然，但事实的确如 此。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.025996750406199226,
      0.4231111111111111,
      0.9498812648418947,
      0.5875555555555556
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_4630",
    "order": 4
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_4630_4",
    "text": "• 篇作可以直接决定考的命运。先不说内容写得多好，最起码不要在基本点上出现 纰漏。哪怕功，也有个40多分，但绝不能有过，那样可能就是20、30分了。",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.024996875390576177,
      0.6151111111111112,
      0.953880764904387,
      0.7253333333333334
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_4630",
    "order": 5
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_4630_5",
    "text": "●但很多考还是不清不，“作死”的做法在应付。下盘点下考场作常见的种 “作死”做法，你中招了吗？",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.027496562929633796,
      0.7484444444444445,
      0.9533808273965755,
      0.8568888888888889
    ],
    "page": "yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_4630",
    "order": 6
  },
  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_yanbaopptmerge_yanbaoPPT_4630_6",
    "text": "返些，是老师可以教会学生，而学生也完全可以规避的！",
    "canon_role": "support_paragraph",
    "bbox": [
      0.06499187601549807,
